# Bug Reports Directory

This folder contains AI-analyzed bug reports stored as markdown files.

## Structure
```
bug-reports/
  YYYY-MM/
    BR-YYYY-MM-DD-####-slug.md
  attachments/
    BR-YYYY-MM-DD-####/
      screenshot.jpg
      console-errors.log
```

## Workflow
1. User submits bug report via the app
2. AI analyzes the bug and generates a fix prompt
3. A PR is opened with the .md file
4. When the bug is fixed, delete the file from the admin panel
